<span id="freeTextContainer16337506978880785400">The saving grace of this story is the backstory of Bianca and her demise. I&apos;ve decided that learning about Bianca is what keeps me reading this series. I really didn&apos;t care for Lilah&apos;s love story (or Lilah... what a twit).</span>
  <span id="freeText16337506978880785400" style="display:none">The saving grace of this story is the backstory of Bianca and her demise. I've decided that learning about Bianca is what keeps me reading this series. I really didn't care for Lilah's love story (or Lilah... what a twit).</span>
