<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer400200956335432598">Nora Roberts is the #1 New York Times bestselling author of more than 200 novels, including Hideaway, Under Currents, Come Sundown, The Awakening, Legacy, and coming in November 2021 -- The Becoming -- the second book in The Dragon Heart Legacy. She is also the author of the futuristic suspense In Death series written under the pen name <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/17065.J_D__Robb' title='J.D. Robb' rel='nofollow noopener'>J.D. Robb</a>. There are more than 500 million copies of her book</span>
  <span id="freeText400200956335432598" style="display:none">Nora Roberts is the #1 New York Times bestselling author of more than 200 novels, including Hideaway, Under Currents, Come Sundown, The Awakening, Legacy, and coming in November 2021 -- The Becoming -- the second book in The Dragon Heart Legacy. She is also the author of the futuristic suspense In Death series written under the pen name <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/17065.J_D__Robb" title="J.D. Robb" rel="nofollow noopener">J.D. Robb</a>. There are more than 500 million copies of her books in print. </span>
  <a data-text-id="400200956335432598" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
